Package: repopath-sanitizer
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3-pyqt6, git
Description: Scan and fix Git working tree paths for Windows checkout
 RepoPath Sanitizer scans a local Git working tree on Linux and detects file/folder
 names that would fail on Windows. It proposes fixes and can apply safe git-aware
 renames (git mv) to preserve history.
